(983, 4, 86, '《算法》菲波那切数列', '', '/upload/201708/28/time.jpg', 'A:农场买了一只羊,第一年是小羊,第二年底生一只,第三年不生,第四年底再生一只,第五年死掉.(找规律)羊的总数:1, 2, 2, 4, 3, 6, 5,10, 8, 16, 13, 26, 21, 42, …奇数年为 1, 2, 3, 5, 8 Fib((n + 1) / 2) 偶数年为 2, 4, 6, 10, 16 Fib(n / 2) * 2// 函数:获得第 n 年的斐…', '<pre class="brush:js;toolbar:false">A:农场买了一只羊,第一年是小羊,第二年底生一只,第三年不生,第四年底再生一只,第五年死掉.(找规律)羊的总数:1,&nbsp;2,&nbsp;2,&nbsp;4,&nbsp;3,&nbsp;6,&nbsp;5,\r\n10,&nbsp;8,&nbsp;16,&nbsp;13,&nbsp;26,&nbsp;21,&nbsp;42,&nbsp;…奇数年为&nbsp;1,&nbsp;2,&nbsp;3,&nbsp;5,&nbsp;8&nbsp;Fib((n&nbsp;+&nbsp;1)&nbsp;/&nbsp;2)&nbsp;偶数年为&nbsp;2,&nbsp;4,&nbsp;6,&nbsp;10,&nbsp;16&nbsp;Fib(n&nbsp;/&nbsp;2)&nbsp;*&nbsp;2\r\n//&nbsp;函数:获得第&nbsp;n&nbsp;年的斐波那契数,1,2,3,5,8,......忽略最初的&nbsp;0\r\n57\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nvar&nbsp;getFib&nbsp;=&nbsp;function()&nbsp;{\r\nvararr&nbsp;=&nbsp;[1,&nbsp;1];\r\nreturn&nbsp;function&nbsp;fn(n)&nbsp;{\r\nif(n&nbsp;&lt;arr.length)&nbsp;{\r\nreturn&nbsp;arr[n];\r\n}else&nbsp;{\r\narr.push(arr[arr.length-&nbsp;1]&nbsp;+&nbsp;arr[arr.length-&nbsp;2]);\r\nreturn&nbsp;fn(n);\r\n};\r\n};\r\n}();\r\n//&nbsp;获得第&nbsp;n&nbsp;年的羊的总数\r\nfunction&nbsp;countSheep(n)&nbsp;{\r\nvar&nbsp;count;\r\nif(n&nbsp;%&nbsp;2&nbsp;===&nbsp;0)&nbsp;{\r\ncount&nbsp;=&nbsp;getFib(n&nbsp;/&nbsp;2)&nbsp;*2;\r\n}else&nbsp;{\r\ncount&nbsp;=&nbsp;getFib((n&nbsp;+&nbsp;1)&nbsp;/2);\r\n};\r\nreturn&nbsp;count;\r\n};</pre>', 100, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'admin', '2017-08-28 00:00:00', '2017-08-29 19:27:46', '管理员', ''),
