xt-indent: 14px;">webstrom</span><span style="text-indent: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">是英文版的</span><span style="text-indent: 14px;">,</span><span style="text-indent: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">关掉</span><span style="text-indent: 14px;">webstrom,</span><span style="text-indent: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">下面是汉化的方法</span><span style="text-indent: 14px;">.</span></p><p><span style="text-indent: 14px;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051923243839.png" title="image.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p><p><span style="text-indent: 14px;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051923315788.png" title="image.png" alt="image.png"/></span></p></li><li><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:24px;text-indent:19px"><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">找到</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">webstrom</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">的汉化包</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">,</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">复制粘贴到</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">,webstrom</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">的安装路径的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">lib</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">路径里面</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">,</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">把里面的</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">resources_en.jar</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:red;background:yellow;background: yellow">删掉</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:19px;color:red;background:yellow;background:yellow">.</span></strong></p><p><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051923445086.png" title="image.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051923519423.png" title="image.png" alt="image.png"/></p></li><li><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-indent: 21px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;">重新打开</span><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-indent: 21px; font-size: 21px;">webstrom,ok</span><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-indent: 21px; font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;">了</span><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); text-indent: 21px; font-size: 21px;">!!!</span><br/></p></li></ol><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:24px;text-indent:21px"><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:24px;text-indent:21px"><br/></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:24px;text-indent:0"><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p>', 99, 5, 0, 1, NULL, 0, 0, 'wucaimei', '2017-08-05 19:24:55', NULL, '管理员', ''),
(47, 1, 58, 'Webstrom常见使用问题,字体大小,字体乱码,多行操作等', '', '//logo.png', '1.    Webstrom的代码字体太小了……肿么办?????快捷键:CTRL+ALT+S,调出设置面板,   或者鼠标左键点击菜单栏的”文件”,找到设置选项,调出设置面板.2.界面字体大小,下面框住这些就是界面字体大小….Ctrl+Alt+S调出设置面板3.webstrom的界面文字，乱码了，怎么办？？…', '<p><span style="background-color: yellow;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Webstrom的代码字体太小了……肿么办?????</span></p><p>à快捷键<span style="color: red;">:CTRL+ALT+S</span>,调出设置面板,&nbsp;&nbsp;或者鼠标左键点击<span style="color: red;">菜单栏</span>的”<span style="color: red;">文件</span>”,找到<span style="color: red;">设置</span>选项,调出<span style="color: red;">设置</span>面板.</p><p><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051928138134.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><br></p><p>2.<span style="background-color: yellow;">界面字体大小,下面框住这些就是界面字体大小….</span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051928470138.png" alt="image.png"></span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">Ctrl+Alt+S调出设置面板</span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051929077342.png" alt="image.png"></span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">3.webstrom的界面文字，乱码了，怎么办？？？</span></p><p>Ctrl+Alt+s调出设置面板</p><p><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051929408162.png" alt="image.png"></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;webstrom怎么可以自动格式化代码吗？？？。。。。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;">&nbsp;</span></p><p>自动做不到。。。手动可以。。。Ctrl+Alt+L</p><p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="background-color: yellow;">选择前景色</span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051932344702.png" alt="image.png" height="177" width="752"></span></p><p><span style="background-color: yellow;"><img src="/upload/201708/05/201708051932457505.png" alt="image.png"></span></p><p><strong style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">6.</strong><strong style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125);">复制一整行,Ctrl+D</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125);">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Alt+鼠标点击&nbsp;&nbsp;选中多行操作</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 99, 1, 0, 1, NULL, 1, 0, 'wucaimei', '2017-08-05 19:34:10', '2017-09-26 20:10:40', '管理员', ''),
